cdata.name: Bata
cdata.desc:
Bata (BTA) is a peer-to-peer currency that enables instant, near-zero cost payments to anyone in the world. BTAis an open source, global payment network that is fully decentralized without any central authorities. Mathematics secures the network and empowers individuals to control their own finances. BTAfeatures faster transaction confirmation times and improved storage efficiency than the leading math-based currencies. BTAhassubstantial industry support, trade volume and liquidity, BTA is a proven medium of commerce complementary to Bitcoin (BTC).
